name: Alpha Distribution & Services (M) Sdn. Bhd.
overview:
Alpha Distribution & Services Sdn. Bhd. was established with trade name Alpha Supplies Trading (AST) in 1985. The company quickly grew to become one of the top IT & Office supplies company in the east region of Malaysia, serving major corporate customers ranging from Multi National Companies (MNC) to Small & Medium Enterprise (SME) and various government bodies around the region.

Our product ranges from Epson Receipt Printer, Datamax Barcode Printer, Datalogic Sanners, Casio Mobile Computer, O’Neil Mobile Printer, Zebra Mobile, Pre-Programmable Keyboards, and wide range of business to consumer products. Up to date, the company successfully increased it’s retail base up to 361 channels across Asia, in the east region of Malaysia, neighbouring countries including Indonesia, Phillippines and Singapore.
